message:
"Of the 6824424 pages we tested on the site over the past 90 days, 1687 page(s) resulted in malicious software being downloaded and installed without user consent. The last time Google visited this site was on 2015-01-23, and the last time suspicious content was found on this site was on 2015-01-23.

Malicious software includes 139894 exploit(s), 2751 trojan(s), 503 virus. Successful infection resulted in an average of 5 new process(es) on the target machine."
story: Mohammad Alaggan shared a link to the group: Egyptian Geeks.
